###obtener circuitos
GET http://localhost:3000/api/circuits

###crear circuito
# @name createCircuit
POST http://localhost:3000/api/circuits
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Madring",
  "description": "Circuito de Formula 1",
  "abbreviation": "Madring F1",
  "status": "active"
}

### ID
@id = {{createCircuit.response.body.data.id}} 

###obtener circuito por id
GET http://localhost:3000/api/circuits/{{id}}


